SUB_W01_EVAR_SIUG_SEQUOIA_HOKORA_020_CUT.text:
Stop. That talisman protects the castle;
this man is speaking falsehoods in an
attempt to deceive you.

SUB_W01_EVAR_SIUG_JIZO_020_CUT_000_020.text:
This is a place for children;
I imagine you came here to frolic
when you were yet small?

SUB_W01_EVAR_SIUG_AMANO_IWATO_000_CUT_00.text:
I suppose that's one way of looking at it;
it's not terrible to do things your own way.
I rather enjoyed traveling with you. Farewell.
